st suite (4772 passed) and Ruff are clean. Mypy errors in `cli.py` are pre-existing and unrelated to this task's documentation-focused changes.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [ ] None — severity: N/A\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe documentation is well-integrated and the opt-in live test provides a solid baseline for future router connectivity verification.\n"}}
